Ole Dammegård interviews Canadian Counsellor Sandra Fecht about Satanic Ritualistic Abuse, an incredible dialogue with this family counsellor in Ontario Canada.

She is joined by one of her clients, Frances Toes, who has been victim of cult abuse since childhood.

We discuss Sandra’s many years of experience counseling abuse victims, especially those who have been abused by satanic and masonic groups on various levels.
